sub_title: CELTA qualified English language tutor and teacher
summary:
Education professional with 5+ years experience working as an English language support teacher and private tutor for students of all ages and abilities. I am a British CELTA qualified English language teacher living in Haarlem. I teach adults and children (6+) and give weekly tailor-made one-to-one and small group lessons, online lessons as well as intensive courses during the summer. 

I work with international families where English is a first or second language and help children maintain their level of English while being educated in a Dutch or International school. I also help students prepare for exams such as TOEFL, Cambridge Advanced English or IELTs to gain entry to college or University and I help adults with improving their conversational or written English whether itâ€™s needed in the workplace or for social communication.
